      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just not that simple though. \"tiny shifts\" don't fix the fact that I'm fundamentally broken. it's like i'm watching a movie over and over where the ending is always the same. no matter how hard i push, the loop just resets. it's exhausting. i'm just so tired of fighting it.",
